la Nova or Tgraph brand, image, or reputation.</p><p style="text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;"><br/></p><h1 style="padding-left: 6pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;">Order Placement</h1><p style="text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;"><br/></p><p style="padding-left: 6pt;text-indent: 0pt;line-height: 114%;text-align: left;">Orders are placed through the application directly with the Stella Nova establishment point of sale system. Tgraph and other Stella Nova locations are not liable for these transactions, and you should review any such orders with the specific establishment for which you placed the order. Any special requests must be entered via the application, prior to payment.</p><p style="text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;"><br/></p><p style="padding-left: 5pt;text-indent: 0pt;line-height: 114%;text-align: justify;">Orders are authored, then saved, then paid for. Upon payment processing successfully completing, the order cannot be cancelled. Orders that have not yet been paid for can be changed or cancelled within the application.</p><p style="text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;"><br/></p><p style="padding-left: 6pt;text-indent: 0pt;line-height: 114%;text-align: left;">Orders that are not paid for are not fired for preparation. A unique order number is provided in order history and order confirmation for reference by the user or Stella Nova location.</p><p style="text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;"><br/></p><p style="padding-left: 6pt;text-indent: 0pt;line-height: 114%;text-align: left;">Stella Nova and Tgraph cannot be held responsible for orders placed when the user cannot enter the facility in a timely manner, whether that be lines, traffic, store hours, or any other reason. It is your responsibility to order with the proper store location. You, the user, are liable for the accuracy of your orders.</p><p style="text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;"><br/></p><h1 style="padding-left: 6pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;">Refunds</h1><p style="text-indent: 0pt;